## Integration guide (local, gitignored)

Guide source and builder live under `docs/notes/` and `scripts/integration_guide_*` (gitignored — not in the repo). When changing **workflow surface** files tracked in git, review and update `docs/notes/connectwatch-development-guide.md` if commands, CI, scripts, rules/skills, or GitHub steps changed:

- `.cursor/rules/`, `.cursor/skills/`
- `scripts/test.ps1`, `scripts/release.ps1`, `scripts/setup-github-project.ps1`
- `build.ps1`, `update-and-run.ps1`, `update-and-run.bat`
- `.github/workflows/ci.yml`, `tests/e2e/`, `update-manifest.json`

Do **not** update the guide for routine `internal/` app-only changes unless documented workflow/commands change.

After editing the markdown (local):

```powershell
python scripts/build-connectwatch-development-guide.py
# or: .\scripts\sync-integration-guide.ps1 -RegeneratePdf -MarkSynced
```

Check staleness anytime (local): `.\scripts\sync-integration-guide.ps1 -Check`
